I"ù'<p>So did I recently this week when I wanted to explain to him and his classmate how to implement the below exercise. So why not to publish it in English on my new blog?!</p>

<p>The goal is to take an input from the user and draw an empty square bordered by hashtags on the standard output.</p>

<p>Let‚Äôs see a few examples, if you prefer criteria for your acceptance tests:</p>

